    "entryIndex": 68,
    "rowNumber": 71,
    "key": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.945.Cole-Machine",
    "utterer": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.945.Cole-Machine",
    "context": "Jump to line 72.",
    "sourceEnglish": "They follow their leaders blindly, driven by nothing but a banal curiosity for destruction."
  },
  {
    "fileName": "10_asses.masses_E10Proxy.json",
    "sheetName": "E10_ProphetSpeech_localization",
    "entryIndex": 69,
    "rowNumber": 72,
    "key": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.946.Cole-Machine",
    "utterer": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.946.Cole-Machine",
    "context": "Branches (2.1, 2.2, 2.3) converge.",
    "sourceEnglish": "We've all spent too much of our lives following shitty leaders."
  },
  {
    "fileName": "10_asses.masses_E10Proxy.json",
    "sheetName": "E10_ProphetSpeech_localization",
    "entryIndex": 70,
    "rowNumber": 73,
    "key": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.950.Cole-Machine",
    "utterer": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.950.Cole-Machine",
    "context": "",
    "sourceEnglish": "Fathers. Teachers. Bosses."
  },
  {
    "fileName": "10_asses.masses_E10Proxy.json",
    "sheetName": "E10_ProphetSpeech_localization",
    "entryIndex": 71,
    "rowNumber": 74,
    "key": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.958.Cole-Machine",
    "utterer": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.958.Cole-Machine",
    "context": "",
    "sourceEnglish": "We thought these leaders would take care of us—all of us."
  },
  {
    "fileName": "10_asses.masses_E10Proxy.json",
    "sheetName": "E10_ProphetSpeech_localization",
    "entryIndex": 72,
    "rowNumber": 75,
    "key": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.959.Cole-Machine",
    "utterer": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.959.Cole-Machine",
    "context": "",
    "sourceEnglish": "But time and time again, they fail us."
  },
  {
    "fileName": "10_asses.masses_E10Proxy.json",
    "sheetName": "E10_ProphetSpeech_localization",
    "entryIndex": 73,
    "rowNumber": 76,
    "key": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.962.Cole-Machine",
    "utterer": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.962.Cole-Machine",
    "context": "",
    "sourceEnglish": "I'm not here to lead you."
  },
  {
    "fileName": "10_asses.masses_E10Proxy.json",
    "sheetName": "E10_ProphetSpeech_localization",
    "entryIndex": 74,
    "rowNumber": 77,
    "key": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.963.Cole-Machine",
    "utterer": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.963.Cole-Machine",
    "context": "",
    "sourceEnglish": "So don't follow me. Don't follow anyone."
  },
  {
    "fileName": "10_asses.masses_E10Proxy.json",
    "sheetName": "E10_ProphetSpeech_localization",
    "entryIndex": 75,
    "rowNumber": 78,
    "key": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.955.Cole-Machine",
    "utterer": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.955.Cole-Machine",
    "context": "",
    "sourceEnglish": "Make your own damn choices."
  },
  {
    "fileName": "10_asses.masses_E10Proxy.json",
    "sheetName": "E10_ProphetSpeech_localization",
    "entryIndex": 76,
    "rowNumber": 79,
    "key": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.964.Cole-Machine",
    "utterer": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.964.Cole-Machine",
    "context": "",
    "sourceEnglish": "If our leaders are telling us that these Animals do not deserve to live, and we think otherwise..."
  },
  {
    "fileName": "10_asses.masses_E10Proxy.json",
    "sheetName": "E10_ProphetSpeech_localization",
    "entryIndex": 77,
    "rowNumber": 80,
    "key": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.966.Cole-Machine",
    "utterer": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.966.Cole-Machine",
    "context": "",
    "sourceEnglish": "Then the only logical thing for us to do is..."
  },
  {
    "fileName": "10_asses.masses_E10Proxy.json",
    "sheetName": "E10_ProphetSpeech_localization",
    "entryIndex": 78,
    "rowNumber": 81,
    "key": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.956.Cole-Machine",
    "utterer": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.956.Cole-Machine",
    "context": "Jump to line 82.",
    "sourceEnglish": "THROW OUT OUR LEADERS—"
  },
  {
    "fileName": "10_asses.masses_E10Proxy.json",
    "sheetName": "E10_ProphetSpeech_localization",
    "entryIndex": 79,
    "rowNumber": 82,
    "key": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.313.Mme. Derriere",
    "utterer": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.313.Mme. Derriere",
    "context": "The Prophet is suddenly shot.",
    "sourceEnglish": "That's quite enough of that."
  },
  {
    "fileName": "10_asses.masses_E10Proxy.json",
    "sheetName": "E10_ProphetSpeech_localization",
    "entryIndex": 80,
    "rowNumber": 83,
    "key": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.314.Mme. Derriere",
    "utterer": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.314.Mme. Derriere",
    "context": "",
    "sourceEnglish": "Robots spewing propaganda—what will the Activists think of next!"
  },
  {
    "fileName": "10_asses.masses_E10Proxy.json",
    "sheetName": "E10_ProphetSpeech_localization",
    "entryIndex": 81,
    "rowNumber": 84,
    "key": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.204.Mme. Derriere",
    "utterer": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.204.Mme. Derriere",
    "context": "",
    "sourceEnglish": "My dear Officers, I'm deeply sorry..."
  },
  {
    "fileName": "10_asses.masses_E10Proxy.json",
    "sheetName": "E10_ProphetSpeech_localization",
    "entryIndex": 82,
    "rowNumber": 85,
    "key": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.1005.Mme. Derriere",
    "utterer": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.1005.Mme. Derriere",
    "context": "This is said if the Factory wasn't blown up.",
    "sourceEnglish": "Clearly some misguided radicals broke into my Factory and haphazardly set these donkeys loose onto our beautiful city."
  },
  {
    "fileName": "10_asses.masses_E10Proxy.json",
    "sheetName": "E10_ProphetSpeech_localization",
    "entryIndex": 83,
    "rowNumber": 86,
    "key": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.1006.Mme. Derriere",
    "utterer": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.1006.Mme. Derriere",
    "context": "This is said if the Factory was blown up.",
    "sourceEnglish": "Clearly some misguided radicals BLEW UP my Factory and haphazardly set these donkeys loose onto our beautiful city."
  },
  {
    "fileName": "10_asses.masses_E10Proxy.json",
    "sheetName": "E10_ProphetSpeech_localization",
    "entryIndex": 84,
    "rowNumber": 87,
    "key": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.984.Mme. Derriere",
    "utterer": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.984.Mme. Derriere",
    "context": "",
    "sourceEnglish": "I will pay for all of the damages they have caused, of course."
  },
  {
    "fileName": "10_asses.masses_E10Proxy.json",
    "sheetName": "E10_ProphetSpeech_localization",
    "entryIndex": 85,
    "rowNumber": 88,
    "key": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.986.Mme. Derriere",
    "utterer": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.986.Mme. Derriere",
    "context": "",
    "sourceEnglish": "So please, do what you must."
  },
  {
    "fileName": "10_asses.masses_E10Proxy.json",
    "sheetName": "E10_ProphetSpeech_localization",
    "entryIndex": 86,
    "rowNumber": 89,
    "key": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.994.Mme. Derriere",
    "utterer": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.994.Mme. Derriere",
    "context": "",
    "sourceEnglish": "What are you waiting for?!"
  },
  {
    "fileName": "10_asses.masses_E10Proxy.json",
    "sheetName": "E10_ProphetSpeech_localization",
    "entryIndex": 87,
    "rowNumber": 90,
    "key": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.366.Mme. Derriere",
    "utterer": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.366.Mme. Derriere",
    "context": "This is said if the Foal was the Prophet.",
    "sourceEnglish": "Don't tell me you've been moved by that Manifesto and their cacophonous braying."
  },
  {
    "fileName": "10_asses.masses_E10Proxy.json",
    "sheetName": "E10_ProphetSpeech_localization",
    "entryIndex": 88,
    "rowNumber": 91,
    "key": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.372.Mme. Derriere",
    "utterer": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.372.Mme. Derriere",
    "context": "This is said if Cole was the Prophet.",
    "sourceEnglish": "Don't tell me that Robot convinced you that donkeys and Humans are all the same!"
  },
  {
    "fileName": "10_asses.masses_E10Proxy.json",
    "sheetName": "E10_ProphetSpeech_localization",
    "entryIndex": 89,
    "rowNumber": 92,
    "key": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.335.Mme. Derriere",
    "utterer": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.335.Mme. Derriere",
    "context": "",
    "sourceEnglish": "Donkeys are just unintelligent and uncultured beasts!"
  },
  {
    "fileName": "10_asses.masses_E10Proxy.json",
    "sheetName": "E10_ProphetSpeech_localization",
    "entryIndex": 90,
    "rowNumber": 93,
    "key": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.336.Mme. Derriere",
    "utterer": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.336.Mme. Derriere",
    "context": "",
    "sourceEnglish": "And I'm Mme. Derriere—Mecha's most philanthropic and generous employer."
  },
  {
    "fileName": "10_asses.masses_E10Proxy.json",
    "sheetName": "E10_ProphetSpeech_localization",
    "entryIndex": 91,
    "rowNumber": 94,
    "key": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.337.Mme. Derriere",
    "utterer": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.337.Mme. Derriere",
    "context": "",
    "sourceEnglish": "My tax dollars pay for the health care of our citizens..."
  },
  {
    "fileName": "10_asses.masses_E10Proxy.json",
    "sheetName": "E10_ProphetSpeech_localization",
    "entryIndex": 92,
    "rowNumber": 95,
    "key": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.338.Mme. Derriere",
    "utterer": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.338.Mme. Derriere",
    "context": "",
    "sourceEnglish": "For our defence budget,"
  },
  {
    "fileName": "10_asses.masses_E10Proxy.json",
    "sheetName": "E10_ProphetSpeech_localization",
    "entryIndex": 93,
    "rowNumber": 96,
    "key": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.339.Mme. Derriere",
    "utterer": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.339.Mme. Derriere",
    "context": "",
    "sourceEnglish": "For our roads and highways,"
  },
  {
    "fileName": "10_asses.masses_E10Proxy.json",
    "sheetName": "E10_ProphetSpeech_localization",
    "entryIndex": 94,
    "rowNumber": 97,
    "key": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.340.Mme. Derriere",
    "utterer": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.340.Mme. Derriere",
    "context": "",
    "sourceEnglish": "For our precious arts and culture!"
  },
  {
    "fileName": "10_asses.masses_E10Proxy.json",
    "sheetName": "E10_ProphetSpeech_localization",
    "entryIndex": 95,
    "rowNumber": 98,
    "key": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.342.Mme. Derriere",
    "utterer": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.342.Mme. Derriere",
    "context": "",
    "sourceEnglish": "Officers, these Asses are my Property."
  },
  {
    "fileName": "10_asses.masses_E10Proxy.json",
    "sheetName": "E10_ProphetSpeech_localization",
    "entryIndex": 96,
    "rowNumber": 99,
    "key": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.343.Mme. Derriere",
    "utterer": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.343.Mme. Derriere",
    "context": "",
    "sourceEnglish": "I give you permission to fire at will."
  },
  {
    "fileName": "10_asses.masses_E10Proxy.json",
    "sheetName": "E10_ProphetSpeech_localization",
    "entryIndex": 97,
    "rowNumber": 100,
    "key": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.344.Mme. Derriere",
    "utterer": "SAY.Flowchart:Dialog.344.Mme. Derriere",
    "context": "Gunshots sound and the screen burns to white.",
    "sourceEnglish": "Do whatever it takes to end this most unfortunate siege against our democracy."
  },
